        "title": "fix(docker): add optional Claude CLI install and persistent ~/.claude directory",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nAdd optional Claude CLI install and persistent `~/.claude` directory in the\nDocker sandbox image, enabling sandboxed agents to use `claude` CLI commands.\n\n## Changes\n\n- `scripts/docker/sandbox/Dockerfile.common`: Add Claude CLI install step\n- Mount persistent `~/.claude` directory for OAuth token storage\n\n## Evidence\n\n```dockerfile\n# Claude CLI installed and ~/.claude persisted across container restarts\nRUN npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\nVOLUME /home/node/.claude\n```\n\n_AI-assisted._",
